plot: At Obscura Antiques & Oddities Andy Animal pitches Ryan a porcelain flower vase that doesn't smell like roses. Then a photographer wants to shoot Mike & Evan with an ancient skull-camera hybrid and Mike is thrown a huge bone courtesy of the Jersey shore.
title: "Oddities" Skull Camera Obscura
